{"tid":2362074,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子被控前年機場襲警及管有鐳射筆 香淑嫻裁定罪名成立 還押候判","createTime":"2021-01-11T07:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T10:31:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c781ef0f841a64737b84a9a65c90a8d3c28414","tid":2362074,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12813&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BXwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=8018b0cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12813</a><br />\n<br />\n#沙田裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#香淑嫻裁判官<br />\n#裁決<br />\n#0813機場 <br />\n<br />\n區(27)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員                            <br />\n(2)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器                                          <br />\n(3)襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n(1)/(3)被控於19年8月13日，在機場一號客運大樓離境大堂外，襲擊警員 9085及警長 3712 <br />\n(2)被控於同日在離境大堂外管有一支鐳射筆<br />\n<br />\n1424 廣播<br />\n1455 準備開庭<br />\n1456 開庭<br />\n<br />\n【速報】<br />\n控罪1/2成立，控罪3不成立<br />\n<br />\n（詳情後補）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">‼️手足需要即時還押‼️<br />\n以索取一系列報告：2份精神科報告、1份心理報告、1份背景報告<br />\n<br />\n- - - - - <br />\n得悉需要還押後，手足同媽媽都嚎哭</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b1c1708f50a51a1e984bfe711e39e3dcf71dd58c","tid":2362074,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461fe6c96a160b7323e33dd204b8b9bd4b2eb60a","tid":2362074,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c718935522ff9e03ac1870a43b60d72ccda48694","tid":2362074,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66613293345911c34408fec26fcdc90633acb64","tid":2362074,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"控罪1同3一樣既？"},{"pid":"2d1ad43fc7917bff653e8aa46199ae003b5269df","tid":2362074,"uid":138116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f66613293345911c34408fec26fcdc90633acb64","tid":2362074,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"控罪1同3一樣既？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:20:16.000Z","msg":"兩個唔同嘅人"},{"pid":"4deb9c3009af79f9b4fa0268ccd209e3af7546f8","tid":2362074,"uid":55162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"佢好似係用laser pen照狗<br />\n比人告襲警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班狗真係脆弱過張紙"},{"pid":"bbfbe6df5fc04e2efdd29d9efde4cd34b48c4681","tid":2362074,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f66613293345911c34408fec26fcdc90633acb64","tid":2362074,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"控罪1同3一樣既？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"(1)襲擊警員 9085及(3)警長 3712"},{"pid":"6b11420c96380670e36e7e2bda19b00f7c222c95","tid":2362074,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce8fe2b3c8c2c3eb3c4868bb9c528144e60dd47","tid":2362074,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbfbe6df5fc04e2efdd29d9efde4cd34b48c4681","tid":2362074,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f66613293345911c34408fec26fcdc90633acb64","tid":2362074,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"控罪1同3一樣既？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"(1)襲擊警員 9085及(3)警長 3712"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"同一條罪可以告幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846b74c6ae7066d610f6b059e2220d6c32328f1d","tid":2362074,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5721a34f4bda7b491e91c60d97e881765eda2ac9","tid":2362074,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ce8fe2b3c8c2c3eb3c4868bb9c528144e60dd47","tid":2362074,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbfbe6df5fc04e2efdd29d9efde4cd34b48c4681","tid":2362074,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f66613293345911c34408fec26fcdc90633acb64","tid":2362074,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"控罪1同3一樣既？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"(1)襲擊警員 9085及(3)警長 3712"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"同一條罪可以告幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"畫家之前七條襲警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b543e4762ab34ce109f3c74b167cee7c0a9e6e","tid":2362074,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736691ad0348a312bfacbf0c21f966697406db23","tid":2362074,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香臭西 d logic真係<br />\n雷射筆係武器，但藍屍鐵通就唔係"},{"pid":"ad8bb1b9f40253fc5bd617768255b57ab088444c","tid":2362074,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:04:49.000Z","msg":"香官裁決時指，警長 3712的證供誠實可靠，遂接納其當日的確被被告區得福的雷射筆發出的光束射中。另香官不接納區的口供，稱他的供詞不合情理的地方比比皆是。如區稱因見到示威者用雷射筆，所以他才會帶雷射筆到現場。惟區當日上午9時30分已到達現場，沒可能知道示威者會用到雷射筆，並質疑稱「日光日白，點解要帶雷射筆去照明」。香官因而認為區管有雷射筆的唯一原因是用以傷害警察，終裁定其一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪及一項襲警罪成。"},{"pid":"716416eadf36601e80baf5857707360330b5a46f","tid":2362074,"uid":84751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"香左佢啦"},{"pid":"c3423f96c1776a8bf3175ee290338a21bfb8dc05","tid":2362074,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:14:31.000Z","msg":"官：現場片段受眾多因素影響   未有拍到案發經過不足為奇<br />\n<br />\n裁判官表示，由於閉路電視及現場片段受鐳射筆照射角度、拍攝者角度、群眾非靜止及事發時間短暫等因素所影響，故沒有拍到鐳射光落在李智健面上，以及鐳射光出自被告手中的鐳射筆，亦不足為奇。<br />\n<br />\n官指被告自辯說法不合理  即使智商不高   亦應懂得分辨對錯<br />\n<br />\n相反，被告自辯時不合情理的說法比比皆是。他在審訊時提到，早在案發前一個月購入鐳射筆，但由於他所入住的宿舍燈火通明，故很少使用，因案發當日見到群眾帶同鐳射筆到場，故他亦仿效他人。惟裁判官質疑，被告於早上 9 時半到場，又何以會知道其他示威者會攜帶鐳射筆。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官認為，即使被告智商不高，但他中三輟學後，成功修畢毅進課程，其後亦曾任職侍應數年，理應具備能力分辨對錯，故不接納其證供，並裁定他襲擊李智健及在公眾地方管有鐳射筆罪成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/813-%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4-%E8%BC%95%E5%BA%A6%E6%99%BA%E5%8A%9B%E9%9A%9C%E7%A4%99%E7%94%B7-%E8%97%8F%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E6%AF%8D%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E5%9A%8E%E5%93%AD-%E5%AE%98-%E6%99%BA%E5%8A%9B%E4%BD%8E%E4%B8%8B%E4%BA%A6%E6%87%89%E6%87%82%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E5%B0%8D%E9%8C%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F813-%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E8%25BC%2595%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%259A%259C%25E7%25A4%2599%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%259A%258E%25E5%2593%25AD-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%258A%259B%25E4%25BD%258E%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25BA%25A6%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%2587%2582%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25BE%25A8%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%258C%25AF%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BXwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=db035eca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F813-%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E8%25BC%2595%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%259A%259C%25E7%25A4%2599%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%259A%258E%25E5%2593%25AD-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%258A%259B%25E4%25BD%258E%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25BA%25A6%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%2587%2582%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25BE%25A8%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%258C%25AF%2F&h=4168020d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/813-%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4-%E8%BC%95%E5%BA%A6%E6%99%BA%E5%8A%9B%E9%9A%9C%E7%A4%99%E7%94%B7-%E8%97%8F%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E6%AF%8D%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E5%9A%8E%E5%93%AD-%E5%AE%98-%E6%99%BA%E5%8A%9B%E4%BD%8E%E4%B8%8B%E4%BA%A6%E6%87%89%E6%87%82%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E5%B0%8D%E9%8C%AF/</a>"},{"pid":"877ad5daf3421e08406769196264e47e049665b5","tid":2362074,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:27:05.000Z","msg":"鑑於被告精神狀況及智力問題，裁判官決定先為他索取兩份精神科報告、一份心理專家報告，以及一份背景報告，押後至本月 25 日判刑，其間被告須還押。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/813-%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4-%E8%BC%95%E5%BA%A6%E6%99%BA%E5%8A%9B%E9%9A%9C%E7%A4%99%E7%94%B7-%E8%97%8F%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E6%AF%8D%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E5%9A%8E%E5%93%AD-%E5%AE%98-%E6%99%BA%E5%8A%9B%E4%BD%8E%E4%B8%8B%E4%BA%A6%E6%87%89%E6%87%82%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E5%B0%8D%E